00:27:28,660 --> 00:27:30,716
You're feeling high since you've become a CD?

362
00:27:30,717 --> 00:27:31,659
Of course.

363
00:27:31,659 --> 00:27:34,820
When there's good news, you're high, and when there's bad news, you're down.

