00:28:36,383 --> 00:28:38,117
 Pardon? 

381
00:28:42,356 --> 00:28:44,190
 This? 

382
00:28:52,053 --> 00:28:54,033
 Are you okay? 

383
00:28:55,569 --> 00:28:57,637
 CD Go Ah In? 

384
00:29:07,670 --> 00:29:11,920
   

